This was above average for me, 7/10. Kamitas story without femdom or an ugly bastard is simply fantastic. Probably would’ve been an 8 if: Hikomas story wasn’t so...NTR-y? It’s got the whole “guy watches girl get fucked” vibe and not in a voyeuristic sense; and if Sabakus story at the end had been been a proper 20+ Doujin, it’s premise is absurdly hot and the ending had so much potential to be an actual story. I appreciated that most of vanilla stories had then sex get a bit rough or fast, it really helps (IMO) a doujin to feel more “spicy” than just the 80th missionary, kissing, handholding, other stuff I usually get bored of in vanilla. Anyway, happy new year to my fellow lolicons. Let’s look forward to what this year has in store from our favorite artists!
